{"word":"ἀρεστός","slug":"ἀρεστός","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀρεστός</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἀρέσκω'><el>ἀρέσκω</el></a>\n<p/><i>acceptable, pleasing</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b> <a href='S:Adverb'>adv.</a>, <el>ἑωυτῶι ἀρεστῶς</el> <i>quite</i> to his own <i>satisfaction</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/>"}]}